Package sx.blah.discord.handle.audio

This package contains all audio-related components.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAudioManager
    This class centralizes all audio handling.
    IAudioProcessor
    This represents an audio processor (something that manipulates raw audio data before it is sent to discord).
    IAudioProvider
    This represents a class which can provide audio to discord.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IAudioProvider.AudioEncodingType
    The types of specific audio handling Discord4J supports.

Package sx.blah.discord.handle.audio Description

This package contains all audio-related components. See the sx.blah.discord.handle.audio.impl package for default implementations of interfaces and sx.blah.discord.util.audio package for extra implementations of interfaces.
